ASTral — Structured code retrieval for AI agents

This project is a .NET rewrite of jCodeMunch-MCP by J. Gravelle,
originally available at https://github.com/jgravelle/jcodemunch-mcp.

The original work is licensed under a dual-use license (see below).
This derivative work complies with the non-commercial license terms.

