================================================================================
DERIVATIVE WORK — MODIFICATIONS BY ATYPICAL CONSULTING
================================================================================

Copyright (c) 2026 Philippe Matray / Atypical Consulting

The following modifications were made to the original jCodeMunch-MCP:

  - Complete rewrite from Python to C# / .NET 10
  - Added Kotlin language support (.kt, .kts)
  - Added configuration file support (.astralrc)
  - Added structured logging (Microsoft.Extensions.Logging)
  - Added file watcher for automatic re-indexing
  - Added force re-index parameter with timing metadata
  - Added NuGet global tool packaging
  - Added tool integration tests (xunit v3)
  - Various bug fixes and performance improvements

These modifications are provided under the same dual-use license terms as the
original work (see above). Commercial use of this derivative work also requires
a commercial license from J. Gravelle for the portions derived from the
original jCodeMunch-MCP.
